97,"uid":18604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T23:51:23.000Z","msg":"哦 出囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成日淨係識放風<br />\n畀世界睇下 這就是支那"},{"pid":"49d7b401c4e9ccfbe2e69e13aa8c18562b5dcd62","tid":1473397,"uid":129739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T23:51:51.000Z","msg":"source?"},{"pid":"65acd1c310d2a69dbf0186aa90ce5c73cf6aa13f","tid":1473397,"uid":301152,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T23:53:22.000Z","msg":"軍同警係兩個體系<br />\n武警洗撚跟駐軍法<br />\n香港警察同大陸公安一直都有警務合作<br />\n話就話唔參與行動<br />\n但人員可以提供協助<br />\n但協助嘅定義好模糊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b9ffdc7eec9e73fcc626997b888d5eca46af397","tid":1473397,"uid":137725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T23:54:31.000Z","msg":"外族人往死裡打"},{"pid":"d2f250077f1a0035657a6a04b0b13d27ca4f28d9","tid":1473397,"uid":288765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T00:01:53.000Z","msg":"我係唔會驚"},{"pid":"dc741d493544b63068ed44b53daf83bc21dca6b5","tid":1473397,"uid":274149,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T00:14:43.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">好驚，所以大家換定美金，放係屋企</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"d78f7f341661ff57c87019db7578ca83dc203610","tid":1473397,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f3d9512c4d13b83feb3b951616934df22774e3d","tid":1473397,"uid":194298,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T23:47:34.000Z","msg":"武你老母咩<br />\n駐軍法只係得解放軍一個選項，武警係唔可以在港執法"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T00:36:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />武警係解放軍其中一支分隊<br />\n<br />\n除左 海 陸 空 火箭(二炮) 四軍<br />\n<br />\n第五就係武警"},{"pid":"0315bfe43